{
  "stem": "25209.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I, I think that also, I didn't get stuck into school, because there was this feeling of, hey, this is, this is just temporary.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know, that feeling that the war was finishing-- not that I believed it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I really-- after six years, there wasn't anything that one really believed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But one hoped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So hope started to grow, not, not, not belief.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was like, maybe it's gonna finish one day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing to keep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just survival.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I never hoped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what, what, what would I be hoping for?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't remember anything much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I certainly did not hope that-- no, it was-- the hope would have been useless, really.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Hope would have gotten in the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And kids, kids just survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What am I going to do now?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What am I going to eat now?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How am I going to avoid this big bully now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where are we gonna get some wood so we can keep warm?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to have stealing expeditions to get wood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was survival.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you recall any useful thoughts or, or things that, that kept you surviving?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These books that I read, you know, they were a real antidote.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I-- you know, Byron and Lermontov, they were all-- this is what I-- this is how I heard, heard the thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like, you can stand up and say no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a real antidote to what my mother was saying, was hide.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I never really saw it like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All I know-- all I knew was that I-- I remember, you know, I used to collect-- I used to write down-- every time I read a book, I wrote it down.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
